# Song Tests
Title: Song Tests

## Dramatis Personae

ALICE - A singer
BOB - Another singer
CHORUS - The ensemble

## ACT I

### SCENE 1

ALICE
Before the song, some dialogue.

SONG 1: The Morning Light

ALICE
  Rise with the sun and greet the day,
  let morning light show you the way.
  The dawn is here, the night has passed,
  a brand new day has come at last.

SONG END

BOB
That was lovely.

// Unnumbered song
SONG: A Simple Tune

BOB
  La la la, a simple song,
  nothing fancy, not too long.

SONG END

### SCENE 2

// Song with dialogue mixed in
SONG 2: The Duet

ALICE
  I sing the high notes, clear and bright.

BOB
  And I the low ones, through the night.

ALICE
  Together now, our voices blend.

BOB
  A harmony that will not end.

SONG END

// Back-to-back songs
SONG 3: First Quick Song

CHORUS
  One, two, three, four,
  sing a song and sing some more.

SONG END

SONG 4: Second Quick Song

CHORUS
  Five, six, seven, eight,
  keep on singing, don't be late.

SONG END

ALICE
And that concludes our musical programme.
